ty.%3Cp%3EBlue%20Origin%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EBillionaires%20make%20it%20seem%20that%20we%20have%20all%20the%20tech%20we%20need%20to%20settle%20on%20the%20moon%20and%20Mars.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBut%20the%20hard%20part%20of%20living%20in%20space%20is%20adapting%20the%20human%20body%20to%20extraterrestrial%20conditions.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBusiness%20Insider%20talked%20to%20astronauts%20and%20engineers%20about%20the%20complexities%20of%20space%20habitation.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EPop%20stars%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkaty-perry-blue-origin-space-mission-criticism-career-marketing-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efloating%20in%20zero-G%3C%2Fa%3E%20while%20billionaires%20speak%20of%20building%20cities%20in%20space%20and%20on%20Mars.%20This%20is%20the%20wild%20reality%20we%20live%20in%20that's%20supposed%20to%20help%20pave%20the%20way%20for%20long-term%20space%20exploration%20and%20habitation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20hardest%20part%20of%20living%20in%20space%2C%20however%2C%20isn't%20rockets%20and%20robots%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20the%20squishy%20human%20body.%20Until%20we%20can%20fix%20that%20or%20find%20a%20feasible%20workaround%2C%20life%20beyond%20Earth%20remains%20impossible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20understand%20just%20how%20much%20of%20a%20long%20shot%20life%20in%20space%20is%2C%20Business%20Insider%20spoke%20with%20astronauts%2C%20scientists%2C%20and%20medical%20professionals%2C%20and%20one%20guy%20who%20paid%20%2430%20million%20to%20join%20Russia's%20space%20program.%20Here's%20what%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOnly%20757%20people%20have%20made%20it%20to%20space%20%E2%80%94%20and%20even%20fewer%20have%20stayed%20for%20very%20long.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22photo%20of%20valry%20polaykov%20in%20a%20white%20and%20blue%20cosmonaut%20space%20suit%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6890dd3b3d5881a51c1e8d58%3F