t%20the%20farm%20to%20ensure%20the%20protection%20of%20the%20wildlife.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConsidering%20the%20increasing%20threats%2C%20Gurusamy%20has%20requested%20authorities%20to%20relocate%20the%20deer%20to%20a%20safer%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEchoing%20Gurusamy%E2%80%99s%20same%20thoughts%2C%20Ravindran%20says%20that%20relocation%20of%20the%20deer%20is%20the%20need%20of%20the%20hour%2C%20but%20has%20its%20own%20challenges.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20deer%20is%20a%20sensitive%20animal.%20Even%20a%20shock%20or%20long%20chase%20can%20lead%20to%20tiredness%20and%20can%20result%20in%20death.%20Tranquillisation%20of%20the%20animal%20and%20relocating%2C%20a%20common%20practice%20with%20predators%2C%20will%20not%20serve%20as%20a%20feasible%20alternative.%20The%20relocation%20will%20require%20a%20slow%20and%20long%20term%20plan%2C%20and%20we%20are%20exploring%20solutions%20to%20suggest%20to%20the%20officials%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ravindran%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20uncertain%20future%20for%20the%20deer%2C%20Gurusamy%20says%20that%20he%20will%20continue%20to%20protect%20the%20wildlife.%20%E2%80%9CI%20do%20not%20need%20any%20support%20and%20will%20fight%20with%20the%20farmers%20for%20the%20deer%E2%80%99s%20safety.%20The%20state%20government%20has%20sanctioned%20an%20irrigation%20pipeline%20to%20address%20the%20water%20woes%20for%20the%20farmers.%20Access%20to%20water%20may%20increase%20threats%20for%20deer%2C%20and%20hence%20an%20urgent%20solution%20is%20needed%20to%20reduce%20conflict%20between%20humans%20and%20wildlife.%20It%20would%20be%20appreciated%20if%20some%20experts%20help%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAll%20images%20courtesy%3A%20R%20Gurusamy%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1754649000000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-08-07T123128.971-1754556152.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D483087%22%2C%22s