olitical%20network%20will%20get%20this%20done%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20memo%20said.%20Luckey%20contributed%20over%20%241%20million%20to%20politicians%20and%20political%20committees%20last%20year%2C%20most%20of%20them%20linked%20to%20Republicans%2C%20federal%20records%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20memo%20also%20touted%20an%20Erebor%20cofounder's%20%26quot%3Bunique%20connectivity%20to%20banking%20regulators%26quot%3B%20including%20Jonathan%20Gould%2C%20who%20was%20sworn%20in%20as%20Comptroller%20of%20the%20Currency%20in%20July.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGould%2C%20who%20was%20a%20senior%20official%20in%20the%20OCC%20in%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20first%20administration%2C%20served%20for%20less%20than%20a%20year%20as%20the%20chief%20legal%20officer%20of%20the%20bitcoin%20mining%20company%20Bitfury.%20More%20recently%2C%20he%20spent%20two%20years%20as%20a%20partner%20at%20the%20law%20firm%20Jones%20Day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdam%20Cohen%2C%20a%20top%20Skadden%20lawyer%20who%20worked%20with%20Erebor%20on%20its%20OCC%20application%2C%20recently%20left%20the%20firm%20and%20was%20appointed%20Gould's%20chief%20counsel%20at%20the%20OCC.%20In%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fposts%2Fadam-cohen-5b886325_although-i-am-sad-to-be-leaving-my-colleagues-activity-7356381538902581248-jPD9%3Futm_source%3Dshare%26utm_medium%3Dmember_desktop%26rcm%3DACoAACvuVacBDWr4IE5-rmqIwhnGpiz8AE8zWSo%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELinkedIn%20post%3C%2Fa%3E%20announcing%20his%20job%20change%2C%20Cohen%20thanked%20Gould%20for%20%26quot%3Bthe%20opportunity%20to%20support%20a%20safe%20and%20sound%20banking%20system%20that%20embraces%20innovation%20and%20promotes%20fair%20access%20to%20financial%20services.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20reached%20for%20comment%2C%20the%20OCC%20referred%20to%20its%20general%20timelines%20and%20didn't%20respond%20to%20specific%20questions%20about%20Erebor%20and%20any%20ties%20to%20Gould.%20The%20OCC%20says%20that%20it%20generally%20aims%20to%20make%20a%20preliminary%2C%20conditional%20decision%20on%20charter%20applications%20within%20120%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20OCC%20carefully%20considers%20every%20bank%20charter%20application%20submitted%20based%20on%20the%20facts%20of%20the%20application%20and%20consistent%20with%20its%20statutory%20and%20regulatory%20requirements%2C%26quot%3B%20agency%20representative%20Stephanie%20Collins%20said%20in%20an%20email.%20Gould%20couldn't%20immediately%20be%20reached%20for%20comment%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELuckey%2C%20other%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpalmer-luckey-erebor-bank-executives-list-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EErebor%20executives%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20a%20lawyer%20who%20has%20represented%20the%20bank%20didn't%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpeter-thiel%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPeter%20Thiel's%3C%2Fa%3E%20Founders%20Fund%2C%20which%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpalmer-luckeys-new-digital-bank-erebor-valuation-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%20previously%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20invested%20in%20Erebor%2C%20said%20that%20the%20fund%20%26quot%3Binvested%20a%20relatively%20small%20amount%20(%241m)%20in%20Erebor%20and%20is%20not%20involved%20in%20its%20operations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETodd%20Baker%2C%20a%20senior%20fellow%20at%20Columbia%20University%20and%20a%20consultant%20for%20fintech%20companies%2C%20said%20that%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Enine%20months%20would%20be%20a%20more%20realistic%20timeline%2C%20even%20under%20a%20president%20who%20has%20been%20embraced%20by%20some%20tech%20investors%20and%20cryptocurrency%20advocates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMichele%20Alt%2C%20a%20consultant%20with%20the%20Klaros%20Group%2C%20said%20standing%20up%20a%20bank%20after%20getting%20preliminary%20approval%20usually%20takes%20longer%20than%20three%20months.%20Banking%20regulators%20typically%20won't%20let%20a%20full-service%20bank%20open%20without%20deposit%20insurance%2C%20either%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EErebor%20submitted%20an%20application%20to%20the%20Federal%20Deposit%20Insurance%20Corp.%20on%20July%2028.%20In%20its%20OCC%20application%2C%20it%20said%20it%20would%20proceed%20with%20that%20step%20once%20it%20received%20preliminary%20approval.%20The%20startup's%20fundraising%20memo%20budgeted%20less%20than%20four%20months%20for%20preliminary%20approval%20and%20about%20three%20months%20for%20final%20approval.%20As%20of%20August%207%2C%20no%20approval%20had%20surfaced%20in%20the%20OCC's%20public%20database.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202024%2C%20the%20median%20time%20to%20decide%20on%20a%20deposit%20insurance%20application%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fdic.gov%2Fabout%2Ftransparency-accountability-bank-applications%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E295%20days%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20almost%2010%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBanking%20law%20experts%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20it%20isn't%20unusual%20for%20the%20full%20completion%20of%20both%20processes%20to%20take%20a%20year%20or%20longer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBaker%20said%20he%20believes%20Erebor%20will%20be%20approved%20by%20the%20OCC%20and%20the%20FDIC%20because%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bstricter%20control%26quot%3B%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbank-of-america-trump-conservative-discrimination-debanking-davos-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETrump%20White%20House%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20shown%20over%20agencies%2C%20even%20those%20with%20a%20reputation%20for%20independence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAssuming%20they%20had%20a%20reasonably%20conservative%20business%20plan%2C%20you%20might%20say%20nine%20months%20would%20be%20typical%2C%26quot%3B%20Baker%20said.%20%26quot%3BTo%20the%20extent%20it%20has%20issues%20%E2%80%94%20and%20this%2C%20in%20the%20past%2C%20would%20be%20considered%20to%20have%20real%20issues%20%E2%80%94%20if%20this%20would%20have%20happened%20three%20or%20four%20years%20ago%2C%20one%20would%20have%20expected%20a%20year%2C%20a%20year%20and%20a%20half%2C%20or%20not%20approved%20at%20all.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERegulators%20will%20often%20%26quot%3Bhave%20lots%20of%20follow-up%20questions%26quot%3B%20once%20an%20application%20is%20submitted%2C%20said%20Paige%20Pidano%20Paridon%2C%20a%20former%20staffer%20at%20the%20Federal%20Reserve%20who%20is%20now%20co-head%20of%20regulatory%20affairs%20at%20the%20Bank%20Policy%20Institute.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20number%20of%20commercial%20banks%20in%20the%20US%20has%20been%20dwindling%20for%20decades%2C%20partly%20because%20of%20low%20interest%20rates%20as%20well%20as%20risk-averse%20regulators.%20Fintech-industry%20applicants%20have%20had%20a%20particularly%20tough%20time.%20While%20the%20OCC%20has%20granted%20approval%20to%20one%20fintech%20bank%20in%20under%20two%20months%20since%202017%2C%20and%20others%20within%20its%20120-day%20timeframe%2C%20other%20applications%20were%20withdrawn%20after%20years%20of%20delay.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVaro%20Bank%2C%20an%20online%20bank%20that%20targets%20low-to-middle-income%20consumers%2C%20spent%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.americanbanker.com%2Fnews%2Fvaro-gets-vital-fdic-ok-for-bank-charter%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20reported%20%24100%20million%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20took%20three%20years%20before%20winning%20full%20approval%20from%20the%20OCC%20and%20the%20Federal%20Deposit%20Insurance%20Corp.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsofi-files-application-national-bank-charter-fintech-with-occ-2020-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESoFi%20applied%20for%20a%20national%20bank%20charter%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20July%202020%2C%20pivoted%20in%202021%20to%20acquire%20a%20bank%2C%20and%20received%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.occ.gov%2Fnews-issuances%2Fnews-releases%2F2022%2Fnr-occ-2022-4.html%5C%2