%20CEO%20Tim%20Cook%20and%20an%20Apple%20logo%20on%20stage%20at%20WWDC%20in%20June%202024.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6894c0c6194a2d49b8ae294a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223143%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EApple's%20Tim%20Cook%20is%20pitching%20a%20bunch%20of%20new%20AI-powered%20services.%20Are%20they%20enough%20to%20get%20you%20to%20buy%20a%20new%20iPhone%3F%3Cp%3EJeff%20Chiu%2FAP%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EApple%20CEO%20Tim%20Cook%20set%20off%20a%20guessing%20game%20when%20he%20said%20he%20was%20on%20the%20hunt%20for%20deals%20of%20all%20sizes.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWith%20about%20%24133%20billion%20of%20cash%2C%20Apple%20can%20afford%20to%20spend%20big%2C%20but%20it%20has%20preferred%20to%20be%20thrifty%20so%20far.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBI%20asked%20sources%20what%20companies%20should%20be%20on%20Apple's%20shopping%20list.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EApple%2C%20which%20has%20historically%20been%20the%20quietest%20of%20the%20Big%20Tech%20companies%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20dealmaking%2C%20set%20off%20a%20guessing%20game%20in%20Silicon%20Valley%20last%20week%20when%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftim-cook-apple-acquisition-merger-ai-earnings-ma-startups-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECEO%20Tim%20Cook%20said%20he%20was%20on%20the%20hunt%20for%20deals.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20very%20open%20to%20M%26amp%3BA%20that%20accelerates%20our%20road%20map%2C%26quot%3B%20Cook%20said%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-q3-earnings-aapl-stock-price-iphone-demand-ai-tariffs-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ethe%20company's%20earnings%20call%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20referring%20to%20mergers%20and%20acquisitions.%20%26quot%3BWe%20basically%20ask%20ourselves%20whether%20a%20company%20can%20help%20us%20accelerate%20a%20road%20map.%20If%20they%20do%2C%20then%20we're%20interested.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApple's%20stock%20is%20down%20about%2010%25%20this%20year%2C%20partly%20out%20of%20investor%20concern%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-intelligence-siri-delay-ai-race-assistant-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eit%20has%20fallen%20behind%20in%20the%20AI%20race.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20lot%20of%20pressure%20on%20Apple's%20leadership%20to%20do%20something%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Gil%20Luria%2C%20head%20of%20technology%20research%20at%20DA%20Davidson.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20a%20lot%20of%20what%20we%20were%20hearing%20on%20the%20earnings%20call%2C%20is%20the%20leadership%20team%20acknowledging%2C%20we%20understand%20you%20want%20us%20to%20do%20something%2C%20we%20hear%20you%2C%20and%20if%20that%20means%20more%20investment%20or%20if%20that%20means%20making%20an%20acquisition%2C%20those%20are%20both%20things%20that%20we%20are%20looking%20into.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20about%20%24133%20billion%20of%20cash%20on%20hand%2C%20Apple%20can%20afford%20to%20spend%20big%2C%20but%20it%20has%20generally%20preferred%20to%20be%20thrifty.%20Cook%20hinted%20that%20strategy%20could%20change%2C%20however.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20not%20stuck%20on%20a%20certain%20size%20company%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECook%20said%20Apple%20has%20bought%20seven%20smaller%20companies%20this%20year%20from%20%26quot%3Ball%20walks%20of%20life%26quot%3B%20and%20was%20doing%20a%20deal%20once%20every%20few%20weeks.%20Its%20last%20sizable%20deal%20was%20over%20a%20decade%20ago%2C%20when%20it%20bought%20Beats%20Electronics%20for%20%243%20billion%20in%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20would%20be%20an%20AI%20version%20of%20this%20now%3F%20One%20tech%20banker%20who%20asked%20to%20remain%20anonymous%20mentioned%20AI-powered%20media-creation%20startups%20such%20as%20Runway%20AI%2C%20Eleven%20Labs%2C%20and%20Pika%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApple's%20core%20is%20all%20about%20consumer%20experiences%2C%20creativity%2C%20and%20media%2C%20so%20it%20would%20be%20better%20for%20the%20company%20to%20focus%20acquisitions%20on%20AI%20startups%20that%20help%20it%20make%20progress%20in%20these%20areas%2C%20the%20banker%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20would%20probably%20rule%20out%20startups%20such%20as%20Anthropic%20and%20Cohere%2C%20which%20focus%20more%20on%20enterprise%20users.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20obvious%20company%20here%20is%20OpenAI%2C%20which%20currently%20ranks%20at%20the%20top%20of%20Apple's%20App%20Store.%20This%20banker%20said%20that%20Apple%20should%20have%20bought%20OpenAI%2C%20but%20with%20the%20startup's%20valuation%20potentially%20headed%20toward%20%24500%20billion%2C%20that%20ship%20has%20very%20likely%20sailed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20also%20regulatory%20concerns%20if%20a%20company%20is%20too%20big%2C%20according%20to%20Luria.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20most%20intents%20and%20purposes%2C%20large%20M%26amp%3BA%20right%20now%20is%20off%20limits%20for%20these%20companies%2C%26quot%3B%20Luria%20said%2C%20pointing%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftech-memo-meta-scale-ai-investment-mark-zuckerberg-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMeta's%20Scale%20AI%20investment%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20a%20blueprint%20for%20how%20Apple%20might%20proceed%20with%20a%20partnership%20and%20investment%20rather%20than%20an%20acquisition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESo%2C%20what%20should%20be%20on%20Apple's%20shopping%20list%3F%20BI%20asked%20these%20sources%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EJim%20McVeigh%2C%20a%20longtime%20investment%20banker%20who%20is%20the%20founder%20and%20CEO%20of%20Cyndx%2C%20an%20AI-powered%20platform%20for%20private%20capital%20markets%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EGil%20Luria%2C%20head%20of%20technology%20research%20at%20DA%20Davidson%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EDan%20Ives%2C%20managing%20director%20and%20equity%20research%20analyst%20at%20Wedbush%20Securities%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EJordan%20Thibodeau%2C%20former%20M%26amp%3BA