tting%20that%20food%20is%20indeed%20the%20zeitgeist%20of%20the%20landscape%2C%20Fatma%20says%2C%20there%20is%20so%20much%20more%20too%2C%20that%20Old%20Delhi%20has%20to%20offer.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EPurani%20Dilli%3A%20where%20joy%20is%20the%20common%20denominator%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CGrowing%20up%20in%20the%20vibrant%20lanes%20of%20Old%20Delhi%2C%20one%20of%20the%20most%20captivating%20experiences%20was%20witnessing%20the%20%3Cem%3Ejuloos%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20Abu%20writes%20in%20one%20of%20his%20posts.%20He%E2%80%99s%20referring%20to%20the%20parades%20that%20colour%20the%20streets%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F393444%2Ffestivals-in-india-2025-hemis-festival-nehru-trophy-boat-race-jio-mami-jaipur-literature-festival%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eoccasion%20of%20different%20festivals%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20Abu%E2%80%99s%20most%20priceless%20childhood%20memories%20is%20that%20of%20witnessing%20the%20%3Cem%3ERamlila%20ki%20sawari%3C%2Fem%3E.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20iconic%20procession%20was%20initiated%20by%20Mughal%20Emperor%20Bahadur%20Shah%20Zafar%20for%20the%20Hindus%20of%20Shahjahanabad.%20Despite%20his%20exile%20to%20Rangoon%20after%20the%201857%20revolt%2C%20the%20roots%20of%20this%20custom%20have%20dug%20deep%2C%20allowing%20it%20to%20thrive%20for%20over%20180%20years%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20writes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FDIBC9JIyUQy%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FDIBC9JIyUQy%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%2