%20with%20trees%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20Bholeshwar%E2%80%99s%20most%20unique%20ideas%20is%20to%20mark%20special%20occasions%20%E2%80%94%20birthdays%2C%20anniversaries%2C%20even%20death%20anniversaries%20%E2%80%94%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F99172%2Fikheti-priyanka-amar-shah-urban-farming%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20by%20planting%20trees.%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%9CWhether%20it%E2%80%99s%20someone%E2%80%99s%20birthday%2C%20a%20wedding%20anniversary%2C%20or%20even%20a%20death%20anniversary%20in%20the%20family%2C%20he%20will%20instantly%20pick%20up%20a%20sapling%20and%20plant%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Trunali.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20his%20way%20of%20giving%20back%20to%20the%20planet.%20We%20also%20encourage%20others%20to%20do%20the%20same%20%E2%80%94%20people%20can%20request%20saplings%20or%20borrow%20them%20from%20us%20for%20their%20special%20days.%20It%20becomes%20a%20beautiful%20memory%20that%20grows%20for%20years%20to%20come.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20last%2025%20years%2C%20Bholeshwar%20and%20his%20family%E2%80%99s%20sustained%20efforts%20have%20led%20to%20the%20planting%20of%20over%20one%20lakh%20saplings%2C%20germination%20of%20nearly%201%20lakh%20plus%20seeds%2C%20and%20the%20preservation%20of%20close%20to%20150%20indigenous%20species.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FSonchafa-Plant-This-tree-planted-by-him-25-years-ago_11zon-1754294215-500x889.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22One%20of%20the%20native%20varieties%20Bholewar%20successfully%20germinated%20is%20Sonchafa%20(Golden%20Champa%20%2F%20Fragrant%20Champa)%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FSonchafa-Plant-This-tree