n)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20book%20added%20makes%20the%20circle%20stronger.%20And%20the%20idea%20is%20already%20sparking%20conversations%20about%20similar%20spaces%20in%20bus%20stations%20and%20railway%20hubs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMore%20than%20just%20books%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Bakul%20Foundation%2C%20this%20isn%E2%80%99t%20the%20first%20experiment.%20Over%20the%20last%20decade%2C%20they%E2%80%99ve%20created%20some%20of%20Odisha%E2%80%99s%20most%20innovative%20community%20libraries%20%E2%80%94%20from%20the%20Little%20Tree%20Library%20in%20Forest%20Park%20to%20the%20quirky%20Library%20in%20a%20Fridge%20at%20Ekamra%20Haat.%20But%20putting%20books%20in%20an%20airport%20feels%20different.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAirports%20are%20places%20of%20constant%20movement%20%E2%80%94%20people%20rushing%20to%20somewhere%20else.%20By%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F451825%2Fbook-in-hand-campaign-delhi-free-library-national-reading-day%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplacing%20a%20library%20here%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20they%E2%80%99ve%20created%20a%20pocket%20of%20stillness%20in%20a%20space%20built%20for%20speed.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20reminder%20that%20even%20in%20the%20most%20impersonal%20places%2C%20we%20can%20choose%20to%20build%20culture%2C%20share%20kindness%2C%20and%20keep%20imagination%20alive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20system%20built%20on%20trust%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Flybrary%20runs%20on%20something%20rare%20in%20today%E2%80%99s%20world%20%E2%80%94%20trust.%20There%20are%20no%20glass%20doors%2C%20no%20staff%20monitoring%20who%20takes%20what.%20Just%20shelves%20that%20refill%20because%20people%20care%20enough%20to%20keep%20them%20alive.%20Volunteers%20stop%20by%20to%20clean%2C%20sort%2C%20and%20restock.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-inst